syntaxExplanation:
for i in range(5):
    if i == 2:
        continue  # Skip 2
    if i == 4:
        break     # Exit loop
    print(i)

examples.code:
for num in range(1, 6):
    if num == 3:
        continue  # Skips 3
    if num == 5:
        break     # Stops at 5
    print(num)    # Output: 1, 2, 4
